
Overview of noun bravo

The noun bravo has 2 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. assassin, assassinator, bravo -- (a murderer (especially one who kills a prominent political figure) who kills by a surprise attack and often is hired to do the deed; "his assassins were hunted down like animals"; "assassinators of kings and emperors")
2. bravo -- (a cry of approval as from an audience at the end of great performance)

